{"about_the_game":"Terminal Earth is a <strong>survival road trip.</strong><br><br>The world you once knew turned into oblivion, can you survive it and join other survivors in the eldorado ?<br><br>Just like an escape game, find a way out of this hostile hand crafted open world !<br><br>Features :<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Fight zombies, large mutants and insects. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632060/extras/ezgif.com-gif-maker__7_.gif?t=1731512668\" /><br><br></li><li> Use a large arsenal of weapons (More than 30 different weapons : swords, handguns, rifles, rocket launcher etc...)<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632060/extras/ezgif.com-gif-maker_12.gif?t=1731512668\" /><br><br></li><li> Survive unleashed nature. (Sandstorms, acid swamps, lava)<br><br></li><li> Hand crafted open world.<br><br></li><li> Vehicles are key to survive. (Full physics, deep and realistic gameplay mechanics)<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632060/extras/ezgif.com-gif-maker__4_.gif?t=1731512668\" /><br><br></li><li> Navigate through this world using your map and compass.<br><br></li><li> Explore the world horizontally and vertically. (Each floor from each building can be explored)<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632060/extras/ezgif.com-gif-maker__5_.gif?t=1731512668\" /><br><br></li><li> Use items you loot to craft weapons and tools.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632060/extras/ezgif.com-gif-maker__1_.gif?t=1731512668\" /><br><br></li><li> Solve puzzles to unlock new areas or tools that might help you escape.<br><br></li><li> Carefully manage your vitals, thirst and hunger.<br><br></li><li> Find pieces of lore as old journals throughout the game, encouraging you to explore even more.<br><br></li><li> Day night cycle (With deadly nights)<br><br></li><li> Time is key ! (Resources you loot do not respawn, your time on the map is limited)<br><br></li><li> Atmospheric music tracks <br><br></li><li> Character creation <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632060/extras/ezgif.com-gif-maker__3_.gif?t=1731512668\" /><br><br></li><li> Pet your dog companion !</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632060/extras/ezgif.com-gif-maker__2_.gif?t=1731512668\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632060/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731512668","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632060/page.bg.jpg?t=1731512668","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632060/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731512668","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632060/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731512668","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"The player will meet hostile creatures (Zombies, giant insects) during his adventure. He will have to get rid of them in a bloodshed to keep going."},"detailed_description":"Terminal Earth is a <strong>survival road trip.</strong><br><br>The world you once knew turned into oblivion, can you survive it and join other survivors in the eldorado ?<br><br>Just like an escape game, find a way out of this hostile hand crafted open world !<br><br>Features :<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Fight zombies, large mutants and insects. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632060/extras/ezgif.com-gif-maker__7_.gif?t=1731512668\" /><br><br></li><li> Use a large ars